 panning and classifying; the ASR Outdoor 11pc Clear Pocket Portable Travel Gold Panning Kit includes a handy lanyard for travel and clear hardcase for compact storage</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">KIT INCLUDES: Your pocket gold recovery gold panning kit includes x1 clear hardcase, x1 black rope lanyard, x1 jeweler loupe, x2 plastic dropper pipettes, x1 X14 magnification tweezers, x1 magnetic pick up pen tool, x1 metal testing stone and x4 glass testing and storage vials</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">COMPACT STORAGE: The ASR Outdoor pocket gold panning kit conveniently fits all the gold prospecting equipment and tools in the included clear carrying case for secure and compact storage; the case also comes with an included black rope lanyard for easy carrying</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">TRAVEL FRIENDLY: The small size of this 11-piece gold panning kit, measuring just 4.5 inches wide by 6 inches tall, makes it incredibly travel friendly and easy to tote; whether you’re walking to a local gold prospecting site or embarking on a gold mining road trip adventure, the pocket gold panning gold recovery kit will easily fit into any equipment bag, backpack or general travel bag</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">TOP GEAR EQUIPMENT: All the equipment in this mineral recovery gold panning kit is made from quality material; from the metal magnifying tweezers and durable testing stone to the high-impact plastic hard case, all these gold mining tools will see you through many gold prospecting seasons to come</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>ASR Outdoor Clear Pocket Portable Travel Gold Panning Kit for Prospecting 11pc</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">29.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Get in on the gold rush with ASR Outdoors 11pc Clear Pocket Portable Travel Gold Panning Kit for Gold Mineral Gem Stone Precious Metals Recovery! This portable pocket gold panning kit focuses on mineral, gem stone, precious metal and gold flake or gold nugget recovery, with all the tools you need to extract, assess and store after panning and classifying. Your gold recovery kit includes:\n\nX1 clear hardcase (black rope lanyard included)\nX1 black magnetic pick up pen tool\nX1 x14 metal magnifying tweezers\nX2 plastic dropper pipettes \nX4 glass storage vials\nX1 metal testing stone \nX1 black jewelers loupe \n\nThe ASR Outdoor pocket gold panning kit conveniently fits all the gold prospecting equipment and tools in the included hard plastic clear carrying case for secure and compact storage; the case also comes with a black rope lanyard for easy carrying or for attaching to other equipment or field gear. The small size of this 11-piece gold panning kit, measuring just 4.5 inches wide by 6 inches tall, makes it incredibly travel friendly and easy to tote. So, whether you’re making your way to a local gold mining site or planning a gold prospecting road trip adventure, the pocket gold panning gold recovery kit will easily fit into any equipment bag, backpack or travel bag.\n\nImportantly, all the equipment in this mineral recovery gold panning kit is made from quality material; from the metal magnifying tweezers and durable testing stone to the high-impact plastic clear hard case, all these gold mining tools will see you through many gold prospecting seasons to come!\n\nHappy prospecting, we hope you strike it rich!</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div 